            "text": "Databricks credentials (DATABRICKS_TOKEN, DATABRICKS_CLIENT_ID, DATABRICKS_CLIENT_SECRET) are written to process-global os.environ. In a multi-tenant server, other request handlers or threads can read these environment variables, leading to cross-tenant credential leakage."
          },
          "locations": [
            {
              "physicalLocation": {
                "artifactLocation": {
