            "text": "All tracing integrations (Langfuse, LangSmith, MLflow, Opik) send full user prompts, LLM responses, file URLs, user IDs, session IDs, and error messages to external third-party services without any PII scrubbing or data minimization. This risks exposing sensitive user data, credentials embedded in prompts, and internal system details to external observability platforms."
          },
