          "level": "note",
          "message": {
            "text": "The _seed_to_uuid4 function in the Opik trace integration uses MD5 (hashlib.md5) for deterministic UUID generation. While this is used for identifier derivation rather than security, MD5 is considered cryptographically broken and could lead to collision-based identifier conflicts."
          },
          "locations": [
            {
              "physicalLocation": {
